undit  flashratings does not provide advice our job is to accurately and objectively report on analysts credible research and opinions the only advice flashratings will ever give you is to absorb as much fundamental research and different opinions as possible and make your own decisions  flashratings favors covering analysts with proven track records but will cover all analysts as long as their research is honest and professional sign up » allied world global offices syndicate  allied worldwide careers contact us allied world about us ratings media community investors global offices syndicate  allied worldwide careers contact us insurance list of regions asiapacific australia hong kong singapore europe  uk latin america miami north america bermuda canada usa syndicate  view all insurance products view all insurance products reinsurance list of products facultative general casualty treaty marine  aviation treaty professional lines treaty property lines treaty specialty lines treaty investors trading symbol awh exchange nyse stock quote   agm materials fairfax investor presentation news  fairfax financial successfully completes acquisition of allied world and closes exchange offer  fairfax offer for allied world shares to expire at  pm today  fairfax financial and allied world announce short twoday extension  sp dow jones indices announces changes to the sptsx canadian indices  fairfax and allied world announce final exchange ratio for exchange offer x insurance products list casualty construction  engineering environmental liability healthcare liability marine personal lines programs  delegated authority sme  uk commercial division workers compensation commercial motor crisis management framewrx management  financial lines mergers  acquisitions  wi professional liability  indemnity property  energy surety casualty commercial motor construction  engineering crisis management environmental liability framewrx healthcare liability management  financial lines marine merge